<li id="cite_note-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://h20293.www2.hp.com/portal/swdepot/displayInstallInfo.do?productNumber=SCTP" class="external text" title="http://h20293.www2.hp.com/portal/swdepot/displayInstallInfo.do?productNumber=SCTP" rel="nofollow">"Stream Control Transmission Protocol (SCTP)"</a>. Hewlett-Packard Development Company<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://h20293.www2.hp.com/portal/swdepot/displayInstallInfo.do?productNumber=SCTP" class="external free" title="http://h20293.www2.hp.com/portal/swdepot/displayInstallInfo.do?productNumber=SCTP" rel="nofollow">http://h20293.www2.hp.com/portal/swdepot/displayInstallInfo.do?productNumber=SCTP</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Stream+Control+Transmission+Protocol+%28SCTP%29&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=Hewlett-Packard+Development+Company&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fh20293.www2.hp.com%2Fportal%2Fswdepot%2FdisplayInstallInfo.do%3FproductNumber%3DSCTP&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Stream_Control_Transmission_Protocol"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.qnx.com/developers/docs/6.3.0SP3/neutrino/sys_arch/tcpip.html#SCTP" class="external text" title="http://www.qnx.com/developers/docs/6.3.0SP3/neutrino/sys_arch/tcpip.html#SCTP" rel="nofollow">"TCP/IP Networking"</a>. <i>QNX Developer Support</i>. QNX Software Systems<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.qnx.com/developers/docs/6.3.0SP3/neutrino/sys_arch/tcpip.html#SCTP" class="external free" title="http://www.qnx.com/developers/docs/6.3.0SP3/neutrino/sys_arch/tcpip.html#SCTP" rel="nofollow">http://www.qnx.com/developers/docs/6.3.0SP3/neutrino/sys_arch/tcpip.html#SCTP</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-09-13</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=TCP%2FIP+Networking&amp;rft.atitle=QNX+Developer+Support&amp;rft.pub=QNX+Software+Systems&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.qnx.com%2Fdevelopers%2Fdocs%2F6.3.0SP3%2Fneutrino%2Fsys_arch%2Ftcpip.html%23SCTP&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Stream_Control_Transmission_Protocol"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.sun.com/software/solaris/ds/network_performance.jsp#1" class="external text" title="http://www.sun.com/software/solaris/ds/network_performance.jsp#1" rel="nofollow">"Solaris 10 Operating System Networking — Extreme Network Performance"</a>. <a href="/wiki/Sun_Microsystems" title="Sun Microsystems">Sun Microsystems</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.sun.com/software/solaris/ds/network_performance.jsp#1" class="external free" title="http://www.sun.com/software/solaris/ds/network_performance.jsp#1" rel="nofollow">http://www.sun.com/software/solaris/ds/network_performance.jsp#1</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-09-13</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Solaris+10+Operating+System+Networking+%E2%80%94+Extreme+Network+Performance&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BSun+Microsystems%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sun.com%2Fsoftware%2Fsolaris%2Fds%2Fnetwork_performance.jsp%231&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Stream_Control_Transmission_Protocol"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
